The Prison Was Shut Down After a Massacre | Death Row (2006) | Haunted Horror Movie

Several years ago, a bloody riot of epic proportion ravaged the corridors of the Isla del Roca penitentiary, resulting in the gruesome death of both inmates and guards alike.

2006.  Stars: Jake Busey, Kyle Schmid, Stacy Keach
